<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich Frickenhofer, Schultheiß von Neumarkt in der Oberpfalz, und den Rat der Stadt Neumarkt in der Oberpfalz</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Heinrich Nebel, Vikar bei St. Lorenz zu Nürnberg, um Anweisung des Marquart Schmid von Neumarkt in der Oberpfalz, die Klage vor dem Landgericht zu Hirschberg zurückzunehmen, und verweist auf den Rechtsweg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_227" id="112r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_227_r1l22"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Frickenhofer <expan>Schultheiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd den <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l23">des Rats der Stat cʒu dem <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>markt</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_227_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>Schulth<ex>eiſʒ</ex></expan> vnd <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat <expan>fürgel<ex>egt</ex></expan> / her <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nebell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l25">Vẏcarıer hie beẏ vns cʒu ſant <expan>Laur<ex>encʒ</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">der vns cʒu </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Caplan / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l27">daʒ Jm Markart Smid 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒum </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_227_r1l26">vom </ab></add> <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>markt</expan> ſeine gute auf die lant -</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l28"><expan>ſchranne<ex>n</ex></expan> gen <expan>Hirſſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd Jm doch der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Caplan </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l29">
<del rend="strikethrough">des <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> vor vns v̈mb ſölch ſache darümb Er Jm <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeine </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l30">
<del rend="strikethrough">gute alſo <expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / gern ſein wil / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan></del> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l31"><expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan> Smid <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weẏſen wöllet / daʒ Er von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l32">der klag laſſe / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / vnd ſo wil Jm derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Caplan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l34">des <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> gern 
<add><ab facs="#facs_227_line_1575898423562_1701">hıe </ab></add> vor vns ſein v̈mb ſölch ſache 
<add><ab facs="#facs_227_r1l33">darumb </ab></add> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">als </del> Er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_227_line_1581083442417_134">Jm </ab></add> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> cʒ<gap reason="illegible"/></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l35">ſeine gute <expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_227" id="112r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Frickenhofer,
                            <expan>schultheisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, und den
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des rats der stat czu dem
                                <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>markt</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>schulth<ex>eisz</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>fürgel<ex>egt</ex></expan>
                        her <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nebell, vycarier hie bey uns czu sant
                                <expan>Laur<ex>encz</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        caplan, wie daz im Markart Smid <add>vom</add>
<expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>markt</expan> seine gute auf die
                                lant<expan>schranne<ex>n</ex></expan> gen
                            <expan>Hirssp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> hab. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                        den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan> Smid <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weysen wöllet, daz er von der klag
                        lasse. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und so wil im derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> caplan des
                            <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> gern <add>hie</add> vor uns sein ümb
                        sölch sache, <add>darumb</add> er <add>im</add>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> seine gute <expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hat. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
